                        <p class="text-center certsoft-title">CERTIFICATES</p>
                        <ul class="cert-body">
                            <li>CS50's Introduction to Computer Science</li>
                            <li>Codyssey: The Pursuit of Programming and Creativity</li>
                            <li>Generative Artificial Intelligence, Cybersecurity, Emotional Intelligence, and Job Opportunities</li>
                        </ul>
